BIBLIOGRAPHY

These are the references I used for this article. If you are interested in the topic of sound synthesis, each of them is a valuable source of information.

[1] Taylor series expansion of the sine function on MIT Open CourseWare: https://ocw.mit.edu/courses/18-01sc-single-variable-calculus-fall-2010/resources/part-b-taylor-series/session-99-taylors-series-continued/

